Class JSONSchema

    com.google.protobuf.Message, com.google.protobuf.MessageLite, com.google.protobuf.MessageLiteOrBuilder, com.google.protobuf.MessageOrBuilder, JSONSchemaOrBuilder, java.io.Serializable

    public final class JSONSchema
extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessage
implements JSONSchemaOrBuilder
     `JSONSchema` represents properties from JSON Schema taken, and as used, in
 the OpenAPI v2 spec.

 This includes changes made by OpenAPI v2.

 See: https://github.com/OAI/OpenAPI-Specification/blob/3.0.0/versions/2.0.md#schemaObject

 See also: https://cswr.github.io/JsonSchema/spec/basic_types/,
 https://github.com/json-schema-org/json-schema-spec/blob/master/schema.json

 Example:

 message SimpleMessage {
 option (grpc.gateway.protoc_gen_openapiv2.options.openapiv2_schema) = {
 json_schema: {
 title: "SimpleMessage"
 description: "A simple message."
 required: ["id"]
 }
 };

 // Id represents the message identifier.
 string id = 1; [
 (grpc.gateway.protoc_gen_openapiv2.options.openapiv2_field) = {
 description: "The unique identifier of the simple message."
 }];
 }
